item.title:
Ahead of the 10th ‘Fast & Furious’ movie, Vin Diesel reveals that it might now go all the way to a 12th movie:
“Going into making this movie, the studio asked if this could be a two-parter. And after the studio saw this one, they said, could you make the finale a trilogy?”
item.author: PopBase
